licy compliance and enforcement mobile security physical security premises network security technical and forensic auditing and security information and event management siem the company is planning to evaluate secured andor privileged administrator accounts a federated identity security and single signon solution threat detection technologies siem and centralized directory system initiatives in the next  months it uses symantec as its storage security solution personnel are also responsible for overseeing its internal auditing operations regarding security safeguards the company has regular policy reviews inventory of personal employee and customer data inventory of locations where data is stored documented incident response processes inventory of third parties encrypted mobile devices and malware and virus protection on all devices the company also has a regular compliance review process and a continuous compliance model in place that operates under hipaa isoiec  and sox compliance regimes fhlb uses an mssp solutionary technology to monitor threats across its networks security devices and data  the project management unit is responsible for planning and executing it initiatives focused on replacing legacy systems and implementing innovative technologies within the institution personnel in the department are also responsible for procurement and vendor management operations   the companys it budget is typically finalized in q sector industry financial financial services employees  revenue b fye  breaking news on investment signals date type inside scoop  spending trend topic security company federal home loan bank of indianapolis indianapolis in opportunity a high level source has indicated that information security is a spending priority the organization is evaluating vendors this initiative is taking place companywide the organization uses contingentcontract workers for technology initiatives  project scoop topic telecommunications networks company federal home lo